Author: princesspuppy12
Text: We all make mistakes like that, lol. I don't purge, but if I did, I'd make that mistake.

Author: nakazanie
Text: it's okay! we've all made embarrassing ED mistakes at some point or another  I clogged my grandparent's sink after one xmas dinner (i was 14) and my grandpa had to unclog all my puke while i was dying of shame... never have i ever felt so exposed lol  also one time i snuck a fabric napkin to go purge in a fancy restaurant and left it there like NOT ME (i was like 15 too) thug liiiife
